          "prompt_html": "<h1>NOTE COMPLETION 12</h1><p><strong>Questions 6 - 10</strong></p><p>Complete the notes.</p><p>Use <strong>NO MORE THAN THREE WORDS AND / OR A NUMBER</strong> for each answer.</p><p><strong><em>Possible Holiday Ideas</em></strong></p><p>Top end prices - Italy and France</p><p>Bottom end prices - <blank data-qid=\"q6\"/>, Greece and Turkey (Turkey + Cyprus too far)</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Crete</strong></th><th></th><th></th><th>Hotel Tropicana</th><th></th><th>* 1 mile safe walk on <blank data-qid=\"q7\"/> to beach.</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td>* Nice pool; only a few beach bars and restaurants.</td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td>* Really quiet; not near other tourist destinations.</td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td>Palm Hotel</td><td></td><td>* 2 miles from beach but has a <blank data-qid=\"q8\"/> service.</td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td>* Hotel in quite a busy tourist town: lots of bars, restaurants and discos.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Rhodes</strong></td><td></td><td></td><td>Ocean Hotel</td><td></td><td>* Right on beach: less than <blank data-qid=\"q9\"/> from the rooms.</td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td>* 4 star hotel quite far from main town; eat in hotel; good meals.</td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td>Hotel Spiros</td><td></td><td>* <blank data-qid=\"q10\"/> hotel quite close to beach (5 - 10 mins walk) in small village with small swimming pool.</td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td>* A few restaurants in small, quiet village; not much to do.</td></tr></tbody></table>",
